{"tid":21430,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"HKG 第一個SAMSUNG集中討論區","createTime":"2016-12-03T22:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-18T22:35:53.000Z","uid":53440,"like":5,"dislike":73,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"942e14c04904f430f47d2bcc79a645d956a27dde","tid":21430,"uid":53440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T22:26:46.000Z","msg":"其實呢排***都做得幾好<br />\nS7半年前機皇 到依家電量/相機都係王者<br />\n影相方面 相比起IPHONE甚至更好<br />\n角度更WIDE 光圈更加大<br />\n<br />\n雖然NOTE系係柒左 但係無可奈何***都仲有好多人用<br />\n至少S7到目前為止都算係機皇<br />\n<br />\n希望係LIHKG呢到有個SAMSUNG區<br />\n可以傾下*** 相信唔少拉登仔都有用***<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 小弟用S7 8890<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3142a7bd7e854d3296cb07f4766068bf88b3c75a","tid":21430,"uid":1807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T22:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> bomb"},{"pid":"f53d1df1c14f1cb0b7d0c53b5485c759ec9e6519","tid":21430,"uid":53440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T22:37:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> bomb</blockquote><br />\n回收左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3df1281b22a82ebbd36d4ee9cd1b8db02b5a34","tid":21430,"uid":16985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T22:44:00.000Z","msg":"lihkg 第一個軍事post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b961834db87a154f4cd840363192b644f79e6f05","tid":21430,"uid":53440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T22:48:17.000Z","msg":"不過我覺得S7個MON易裂但唔易花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前由1米高跌落地 面落地先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當時見到都心知不妙 仲要用緊薄身硬殼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知真係碎左 玻璃